    "Description": "~mission(Description)",
    "DisplayDescription": "**** Miners Amalgamated Loc. 163 ****\n******/ 'Stronger When United' /******\n\nRE: ARMED ESCORT\n\nWORK BRIEF:  \nAn urgent comm has arrived from a miner out near ~mission(Location). They picked up a possible threat in the area and are rightly concerned that they will not be able to make it to ~mission(Destination) without an armed ship escorting them.\nDURATION:\nThis is an active situation and needs an immediate response.   \nPAYMENT:\nStandard listed rate once the miner is escorted to their final destination. If hostilities do occur, a combat pay bonus will be issued.\nSPECIAL NOTES:\nThere is a good reason the miner is shelling out for an escort. The area has seen more than its fair share of trouble recently. Do what you have to so my miner comes back in one piece.\nAUTHORIZATION:\nBattaglia, Recco",
